<body>
    <h1>T8 - Technical Document</h1>
    <div class=3D"Section1">
        <h1 local-id=3D"9454b1c7f16a" id=3D"T8-TechnicalDocument-1.Introduc=
tion">1. Introduction</h1>
<h2 local-id=3D"5b8b6844cf7a" id=3D"T8-TechnicalDocument-1.1Purpose">1.1 Pu=
rpose</h2>
<p local-id=3D"65ff81a42b8b">This document describes the complete implement=
ation of a cloud-based DevOps monitoring and database observability solutio=
n using:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"9756b93109a1">
<li local-id=3D"883969304cb5">
<p local-id=3D"7befaf947c1a">Amazon RDS (PostgreSQL)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"39952a4056ce">
<p local-id=3D"0cdb60784860">Amazon EC2</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"f97b1ca7d3f3">
<p local-id=3D"b4d2e9e52f8e">Amazon CloudWatch</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"ffd3a1d7a5f7">
<p local-id=3D"d0389748c027">Amazon RDS Performance Insights</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"a1e93f9e52ae">
<p local-id=3D"06d50943d51a">Grafana Cloud</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"76ab5a8c79dc">
<p local-id=3D"4682c38d7c16">Automated Load Simulation</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"e1fa0dc7b777">The intended audience includes:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"4402889f0655">
<li local-id=3D"ed8b419284f7">
<p local-id=3D"07a6edd4978c">CTO =E2=80=93 For strategic infrastructure val=
idation</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"cfac772ab6d2">
<p local-id=3D"7f36f37feee3">Solution Architect =E2=80=93 For architectural=
 compliance and AWS best practices</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"45e4f3638dc7">
<p local-id=3D"0aae422542c5">DevOps Engineers =E2=80=93 For reproducible de=
ployment and monitoring</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"d3d88e5043cf">
<p local-id=3D"569063e51fbf">Developers =E2=80=93 For performance testing a=
nd analytics</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"8c1ce27c278d">
<p local-id=3D"196b41350c56">Resellers =E2=80=93 For replicable customer de=
ployment</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"2e0703519dee">This document enables independent reproduction=
 of the setup.</p>
<hr local-id=3D"631b65f3fa97">
<h2 local-id=3D"4cf360e582d7" id=3D"T8-TechnicalDocument-1.2Scope">1.2 Scop=
e</h2>
<p local-id=3D"20434073ba00">This document covers:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"04884b62ce82">
<li local-id=3D"c2447e3dfac6">
<p local-id=3D"cb5399db1039">Provisioning PostgreSQL RDS</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"e84a96efd608">
<p local-id=3D"7160216d1cab">Network configuration and security groups</p><=
/li>
<li local-id=3D"a8426a852286">
<p local-id=3D"f0c7178f718e">Data import from SQLite dataset</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"6b16eba668bb">
<p local-id=3D"f87647dd866e">CloudWatch integration</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"b2052293c23a">
<p local-id=3D"6dd216a93472">Grafana dashboards (Infrastructure + Analytics=
)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"4f21bb38aac6">
<p local-id=3D"27fecfac4f57">Performance Insights validation</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"f2bab2e7f687">
<p local-id=3D"9ce6dd60d8f6">Automated database load simulation</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"b10735f2273c">
<p local-id=3D"de494cdd9c55">Observability validation under load</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"319547ff4032">
<h1 local-id=3D"387278e70592" id=3D"T8-TechnicalDocument-2.OverviewofDevOps=
Project">2. Overview of DevOps Project</h1>
<h2 local-id=3D"7d7135f33335" id=3D"T8-TechnicalDocument-2.1Definition">2.1=
 Definition</h2>
<p local-id=3D"a15588065a54">This project demonstrates implementation of a =
cloud-native monitored database system with:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"b0a057c69fcc">
<li local-id=3D"9af1d55e74a1">
<p local-id=3D"1edd399514f8">Infrastructure observability</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"c9718c8bfe15">
<p local-id=3D"265466c354b9">SQL-based analytics dashboards</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"901adf8f17dc">
<p local-id=3D"bfb7226afe34">Performance load validation</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"119f1a05878b">
<p local-id=3D"0facd342ec1e">Automated workload simulation</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"465e392a5732">DevOps practices applied:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"be32b5d78dad">
<li local-id=3D"7ff5b03da16f">
<p local-id=3D"bb2a7dc3ae03">Infrastructure provisioning</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"715430b4b6c4">
<p local-id=3D"a5fceec14196">Monitoring integration</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"8c2bf20f5804">
<p local-id=3D"31325d5d9453">Performance testing</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"10593eac9082">
<p local-id=3D"233f67ff5331">Continuous validation</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"8dcaa80c1388">
<h2 local-id=3D"bb60db9049b2" id=3D"T8-TechnicalDocument-2.2KeyPrinciples=
=E2=80=93AWSWell-ArchitectedFramework">2.2 Key Principles =E2=80=93 AWS Wel=
l-Architected Framework</h2>
<p local-id=3D"97bbda6d45ab">The solution aligns with AWS Well-Architected =
6 Pillars:</p>
<h3 local-id=3D"3b0a529afca5" id=3D"T8-TechnicalDocument-1=EF=B8=8F=E2=83=
=A3OperationalExcellence">1=EF=B8=8F=E2=83=A3 Operational Excellence</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"844502fbf489">
<li local-id=3D"58831a541888">
<p local-id=3D"33d1ff921018">CloudWatch monitoring</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"6497106c1f9a">
<p local-id=3D"dbee754a5cec">Grafana dashboards</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"d0c4b23f2743">
<p local-id=3D"86f314fc9965">Performance Insights enabled</p></li>
</ul>
<h3 local-id=3D"97991ad38082" id=3D"T8-TechnicalDocument-2=EF=B8=8F=E2=83=
=A3Security">2=EF=B8=8F=E2=83=A3 Security</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"2da4bfab8217">
<li local-id=3D"dae5a2addf8b">
<p local-id=3D"786c1fcddb1e">Restricted security groups</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"370d4c5dea6f">
<p local-id=3D"1cb768d87cae">IAM best practices</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"220d3f7f4c96">
<p local-id=3D"2bf833aaa8a2">Database-level authentication</p></li>
</ul>
<h3 local-id=3D"6a6670ebf030" id=3D"T8-TechnicalDocument-3=EF=B8=8F=E2=83=
=A3Reliability">3=EF=B8=8F=E2=83=A3 Reliability</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"113d6bfa11e6">
<li local-id=3D"7dc7c34d27c4">
<p local-id=3D"54bc9e632c24">Managed RDS service</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"dd0a7696009c">
<p local-id=3D"43a447a3220c">Automated backups</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"c88f78bc5372">
<p local-id=3D"53117cd3d7b4">Storage autoscaling</p></li>
</ul>
<h3 local-id=3D"5fabcca052ca" id=3D"T8-TechnicalDocument-4=EF=B8=8F=E2=83=
=A3PerformanceEfficiency">4=EF=B8=8F=E2=83=A3 Performance Efficiency</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"93519d0be6fc">
<li local-id=3D"354e41cbf557">
<p local-id=3D"c56a955b0ddd">DBLoad monitoring</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"aafc9800ccec">
<p local-id=3D"f3ae557c3abb">CPU/IOPS tracking</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"ab12d7bb2f71">
<p local-id=3D"a016fce11c63">Load simulation validation</p></li>
</ul>
<h3 local-id=3D"63c3390626a6" id=3D"T8-TechnicalDocument-5=EF=B8=8F=E2=83=
=A3CostOptimization">5=EF=B8=8F=E2=83=A3 Cost Optimization</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"d80010e3756e">
<li local-id=3D"ab858351f8f2">
<p local-id=3D"bcbe13a58fba">db.t3.micro instance</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"725523de5cf8">
<p local-id=3D"9917ceae9087">Free-tier eligible</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"e08ff1e18ffb">
<p local-id=3D"c36768fb3ee1">Right-sized storage</p></li>
</ul>
<h3 local-id=3D"54d62db0e10d" id=3D"T8-TechnicalDocument-6=EF=B8=8F=E2=83=
=A3Sustainability">6=EF=B8=8F=E2=83=A3 Sustainability</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"4abfa5fbdae0">
<li local-id=3D"704718c4e841">
<p local-id=3D"97ee83c55746">Managed infrastructure</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"a06c5395e802">
<p local-id=3D"4b35d63bee5d">Elastic resource usage</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"e967616d8e19">
<h2 local-id=3D"f0296dad2ca2" id=3D"T8-TechnicalDocument-2.3GoalsandObjecti=
ves">2.3 Goals and Objectives</h2>
<ul local-id=3D"0c053a91f2a0">
<li local-id=3D"c1196f4e59ba">
<p local-id=3D"247d3d6edbd6">Deploy PostgreSQL RDS</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"7871e1a772ca">
<p local-id=3D"ef331235e736">Import structured world dataset</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"d247716b3257">
<p local-id=3D"174ae0e95479">Build real-time dashboards</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"a0dd9299b6a4">
<p local-id=3D"ed53cc9e3326">Monitor infrastructure metrics</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"a108ac9ff68d">
<p local-id=3D"32f222818061">Validate performance behavior</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"96e100a1bf91">
<p local-id=3D"b16ab8f65944">Simulate controlled load</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"70ab3dd66786">
<p local-id=3D"98e0504fd87b">Observe DBLoad impact</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"9bf2744158a6">
<h2 local-id=3D"0bcdfbabfc5c" id=3D"T8-TechnicalDocument-2.4ConstraintsandA=
ssumptions">2.4 Constraints and Assumptions</h2>
<p local-id=3D"10bb9bd41eee">Constraints:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"847fc307cbcc">
<li local-id=3D"c127b043993f">
<p local-id=3D"4ca4d918ae42">Free-tier compatible architecture</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"c5bc7ea36135">
<p local-id=3D"9f925e8388d8">Single-region deployment</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"fbce325e49b9">
<p local-id=3D"4ee7830e37b4">Limited execution time (5=E2=80=936 hours)</p>=
</li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"4d113b0a71a0">Assumptions:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"a3cf0ad505c1">
<li local-id=3D"22f0e1ed0379">
<p local-id=3D"8ec019a82e14">AWS account available</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"ed3285882180">
<p local-id=3D"dce5fca05443">Internet access available</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"0f9e5de8f7fb">
<p local-id=3D"b7e7971d446f">Grafana Cloud free account available</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"d31f44390596">
<h1 local-id=3D"74e4a16a3b68" id=3D"T8-TechnicalDocument-3.ArchitectureandI=
nfrastructure">3. Architecture and Infrastructure</h1>
<h3 local-id=3D"2ca94b0d63a8" id=3D"T8-TechnicalDocument-AWSArchitectureDia=
gram">AWS Architecture Diagram</h3>
<p local-id=3D"b4969a9686ed"></p><span class=3D"confluence-embedded-file-wr=
apper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size"><img class=3D"c=
onfluence-embedded-image image-center" alt=3D"image-20260304-200314.png" wi=
dth=3D"468" loading=3D"lazy" src=3D"01ed4406634253386b01c431383fda4f0e88690=
70d85f2463048c69466c70335" data-image-src=3D"https://iamops.atlassian.net/w=
iki/download/attachments/1816199184/image-20260304-200314.png?version=3D1&a=
mp;modificationDate=3D1772654603566&amp;cacheVersion=3D1&amp;api=3Dv2" data=
-height=3D"447" data-width=3D"1368" data-unresolved-comment-count=3D"0" dat=
a-linked-resource-id=3D"1829896209" data-linked-resource-version=3D"1" data=
-linked-resource-type=3D"attachment" data-linked-resource-default-alias=3D"=
image-20260304-200314.png" data-base-url=3D"https://iamops.atlassian.net/wi=
ki" data-linked-resource-content-type=3D"image/png" data-linked-resource-co=
ntainer-id=3D"1816199184" data-linked-resource-container-version=3D"6" data=
-media-id=3D"c4220372-4b1b-4182-9cea-7a655bb3d8ff" data-media-type=3D"file"=
 height=3D"152"></span>
<h2 local-id=3D"1d8752052c06" id=3D"T8-TechnicalDocument-3.1InfrastructureO=
verview">3.1 Infrastructure Overview</h2>
<p local-id=3D"589f3982c623">Components:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"40a8e7547502">
<li local-id=3D"72f140c07e26">
<p local-id=3D"7eb451a8a26a">EC2 (Ubuntu)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"94bc317f46d8">
<p local-id=3D"22c71deb9c69">Amazon RDS (PostgreSQL)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"867cb01a6519">
<p local-id=3D"d53c27e8096b">Amazon CloudWatch</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"98988b4468bc">
<p local-id=3D"2e77db745041">Grafana Cloud</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"af630140b391">
<p local-id=3D"162ab37de912">Performance Insights</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"b451cce31f28">Flow:</p>
<p local-id=3D"f6a16aa2c7d5">EC2 =E2=86=92 RDS<br>
RDS =E2=86=92 CloudWatch<br>
CloudWatch =E2=86=92 Grafana<br>
RDS =E2=86=92 Performance Insights</p>
<p local-id=3D"c374e15c76fe"></p>
<hr local-id=3D"0b375ba1a563">
<h2 local-id=3D"0fe00e40efa7" id=3D"T8-TechnicalDocument-3.2Environments">3=
.2 Environments</h2>
<p local-id=3D"732edd8f7d7d">Single environment used (Production-like simul=
ation):</p>
<ul local-id=3D"32c5726e2103">
<li local-id=3D"be86e6be28cb">
<p local-id=3D"62a2919183d8">Compute Layer =E2=80=93 EC2</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"b078ba892586">
<p local-id=3D"431199a843c9">Database Layer =E2=80=93 RDS</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"5c999c0fe1c1">
<p local-id=3D"0a81535daec1">Monitoring Layer =E2=80=93 Grafana</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"be99c0517ad5">
<p local-id=3D"47e14e5618ed">Observability =E2=80=93 CloudWatch &amp; Perfo=
rmance Insights</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"bc88c1a40671">
<h2 local-id=3D"27482b4b7933" id=3D"T8-TechnicalDocument-3.4ApplicationArch=
itecture&amp;UserRequestFlow">3.4 Application Architecture &amp; User Reque=
st Flow</h2>
<p local-id=3D"147ad2d5de4c">User =E2=86=92 Grafana Dashboard<br>
Grafana =E2=86=92 CloudWatch Metrics<br>
CloudWatch =E2=86=92 RDS<br>
EC2 =E2=86=92 RDS (Load Simulation)<br>
RDS =E2=86=92 Performance Insights</p>
<hr local-id=3D"b241d566214a">
