<hr local-id=3D"f449c20bc7ad">
<h2 local-id=3D"286ccc2aff2d" id=3D"T8-TechnicalDocument-6.3IncidentManagem=
ent">6.3 Incident Management</h2>
<p local-id=3D"8412130fbbb8">Incident detection:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"8661bffa5454">
<li local-id=3D"cd71daea3f97">
<p local-id=3D"2477ba5ffcb5">Monitor DBLoad spikes</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"f39207d17959">
<p local-id=3D"5abf67a8f923">Analyze Top SQL in Performance Insights</p></l=
i>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"1ebc252b40bf">Root cause analysis:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"65a1c014a3c6">
<li local-id=3D"fe038595242b">
<p local-id=3D"21d1a44a3a09">Query-level insight</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"7ece7a3106a6">
<p local-id=3D"f9046de551b9">CPU vs IO load separation</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"0db20966c2f8">
<h1 local-id=3D"7f96437bb34e" id=3D"T8-TechnicalDocument-7.Security&amp;Com=
pliance">7. Security &amp; Compliance</h1>
<p local-id=3D"7ae0fe5ea994">Security Implementations:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"d47b8f4287b8">
<li local-id=3D"4f0447efb0a1">
<p local-id=3D"4f20d15cb9a0">Security group restricts port 5432</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"7daf2d1f42fa">
<p local-id=3D"f6f740750f8e">SSH access restricted to key-based login</p></=
li>
<li local-id=3D"15638f82181f">
<p local-id=3D"b968353bbf41">Managed RDS encryption</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"37254266e215">
<p local-id=3D"e8bbc9ef632c">Performance Insights encrypted</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"61ac00610c47">IAM:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"033046e97edb">
<li local-id=3D"ac82486608a4">
<p local-id=3D"badbbd1f9466">EC2 minimal privileges</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"bce2389c221c">
<p local-id=3D"1b880f7bcb2b">No hardcoded credentials in production scenari=
o (recommended Secrets Manager)</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"537553fde59d">
<h1 local-id=3D"3e7da87aeccd" id=3D"T8-TechnicalDocument-8.CostOptimisation=
">8. Cost Optimisation</h1>
<p local-id=3D"933482bbf95d">Instance Type:<br>
db.t3.micro</p>
<p local-id=3D"49b7561f38d8">Storage:<br>
20GB GP2</p>
<p local-id=3D"522e47101c75">Estimated Monthly Cost:<br>
~$15=E2=80=9320</p>
<p local-id=3D"2c1b332105c8">Cost Modeling Inputs:</p>
